===Research===
The [[electrical and electronics engineering]] and [[mechanical engineering]] departments have been recognized by [[Anna University]] as collaborative research Centers for PhD Degrees.<ref>{{cite encyclopedia
 | url = http://www.winentrance.com/admission_notification/Sri-Venkateswara-College-Engineering-BE-BTech-Admission-2008.html
 | title = departments as research centers
 | publisher = The Hindu (CBE) April 20, 2008. p.11
 | encyclopedia = 
 | year = 2008
 | accessdate = 2008-05-11
}}</ref>
[[R&D]] is aided by a [[technology]] [[innovation]] Center, which also houses [[SPIC]]'s research center.
===== Forum For Economic Studies by Engineers =====

Forum For Economic Studies by Engineers (FORESE)({{pronEng|f<U+0252>rsi}}),brain child of Professor Muraleedharan,was created to equip engineering students with management skills and to help develop team management and interpersonal skills;to ''nurture young professionals into tomorrows leaders''.<ref>{{cite encyclopedia
 | url = http://mail.svce.ac.in/~forese/f_main.htm
 | title = Forum For Economic Studies by Engineers
 | publisher = SVCE website
 | encyclopedia = 
 | year =
 | accessdate = 2008-03-13
}}</ref>

FORESE is a pioneer in having a national level management symposium([http://mail.svce.ac.in/~forese/f_kptl.htm Kapital]) in an engineering college.<ref>{{cite encyclopedia
 | url = http://mail.svce.ac.in/~forese/f_abts.htm
 | title = Pioneers in having a Management Forum in an engineering college
 | publisher = SVCE website
 | encyclopedia = 
 | year =
 | accessdate = 2008-03-13
}}</ref> FORESE also conducts [http://mail.svce.ac.in/~forese/f_mpts.htm Mock Placements]<ref>{{cite encyclopedia
 | url =http://chennaionline.com/education/Events/2007/02article02.asp
 | title = See also: An article on mock placements in SVCE
 | publisher = Chennai online
 | encyclopedia = 
 | year =2007
 | accessdate = 2008-05-07
}}</ref>  and several expert lectures.

==Alumni==

The first ever batch of students passed out in 1989.The alumni of the institution have been successfully placed in several top companies across the globe,and its students have completed Master's and PhD's from prestigious universities that include the [[University of Michigan, Ann Arbor]], [[Harvard Medical School]], [[University of Florida|University of Florida at Gainesville]], [[University of Illinois at Urbana-Champaign]], [[MIT]], [[University of Texas at Austin]],[[Texas A&M University]], [[Stanford University]], [[University of Wisconsin-Madison]] and [[Carnegie Mellon University]].<ref>{{cite encyclopedia
